&lt;h2 id="3实体化描边"&gt;3.实体化描边
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;（面试题）用blender等dcc软件实体化描边比在引擎中用shader实时描边的优势？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;原问：“你为什么用shader实时描边，而不是在blender中用实体化描边？这样不是性能更好吗？”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我：……&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216120501350.png"
width="590"
height="622"
srcset="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216120501350_hu_3e71abace6dffdda.png 480w, https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216120501350_hu_834742a32a8512cd.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20251216120501350"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="94"
data-flex-basis="227px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1）打开一个简单的 箭头网格体。将节点改成着色器-自发光（只是为方便查看效果，没有特别的作用）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140608280.png"
width="377"
height="300"
srcset="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140608280_hu_3f114c97cea62248.png 480w, https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140608280_hu_7bbcf8b3f7865431.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20251216140608280"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="125"
data-flex-basis="301px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2）新建第二个材质，也是自发光节点。材质命名为”描边“，该材质定义描边颜色。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140718087.png"
width="233"
height="233"
srcset="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140718087_hu_87f8195952cbd3b9.png 480w, https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140718087_hu_a21d256a1f1ac417.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20251216140718087"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="100"
data-flex-basis="240px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;注意：描边材质勾选 &lt;strong&gt;“背面剔除”（Backface Culling）&lt;/strong&gt;。这能隐藏材质正对摄像机的正面，只让我们从模型侧面和背面看到它，这是形成描边的关键。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141708968.png"
width="193"
height="458"
srcset="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141708968_hu_6ab293119f46ad4d.png 480w, https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141708968_hu_fdf62e328c7f7877.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20251216141708968"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="42"
data-flex-basis="101px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3）添加修改器——生成——实体化&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140753116.png"
width="325"
height="426"
srcset="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140753116_hu_10e58c7d9b7865c9.png 480w, https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140753116_hu_a63de214e7996996.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20251216140753116"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="76"
data-flex-basis="183px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1：法向翻转；&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;翻转&lt;/strong&gt;：在“法向”选项中勾选&lt;strong&gt;翻转&lt;/strong&gt;。这会使模型背面可见，与“背面剔除”的描边材质配合形成描边&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2：添加材质偏移&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140929458.png"
width="190"
height="474"
srcset="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140929458_hu_8cfe64ce4f1243c6.png 480w, https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216140929458_hu_aefc3b48b363dc74.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20251216140929458"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="40"
data-flex-basis="96px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;材质偏移&lt;/strong&gt;：如果模型有多个材质槽，将此参数设置为&lt;strong&gt;1&lt;/strong&gt;，可使实体化修改器使用材质列表中排在下一个（索引号+1）的材质，也就是我们刚刚创建的描边材质。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最后，只需要调整厚（宽）度就可以查看到描边的效果。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141006557.png"
width="441"
height="206"
srcset="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141006557_hu_ce4956710938d2fa.png 480w, https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141006557_hu_a38ef58e338a0a29.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20251216141006557"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="214"
data-flex-basis="513px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;转到游戏引擎内使用标准着色器会更明显：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141044658.png"
width="298"
height="232"
srcset="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141044658_hu_e38a5c7bcf65c968.png 480w, https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141044658_hu_55498b5a1e28ca34.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20251216141044658"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="128"
data-flex-basis="308px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141901629.png"
width="387"
height="183"
srcset="https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141901629_hu_2e40637e6d5dcb0d.png 480w, https://Selaphina.github.io/p/blender%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82/image-20251216141901629_hu_a9087833f825d538.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20251216141901629"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="211"
data-flex-basis="507px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;法线外扩与背面显示&lt;/strong&gt;：当勾选“翻转”法线后，模型表面的&lt;strong&gt;背面&lt;/strong&gt;变得可见。实体化修改器根据厚度值，沿着模型顶点的法线方向创造出一个新的、略大一圈的“外壳”。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;材质赋予与正面剔除&lt;/strong&gt;：我们将设置了“背面剔除”的黑色材质赋予这个新外壳。这意味着，从这个外壳的&lt;strong&gt;正面&lt;/strong&gt;（即朝向摄像机的方向）看，它是“透明”的；但从其&lt;strong&gt;背面&lt;/strong&gt;（即边缘部分）看，它显示为描边颜色。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>